'''Rub<U+00E9>n Uriza''' ([[May 27]], [[1919]] &ndash; [[September 30]], [[1992]]) was a [[Mexico|Mexican]] [[show jumping]] champion, and Olympic champion. He participated at the [[1948 Summer Olympics]] in [[London]] where he won a gold medal in ''Team Jumping'' as a member of the Mexican winning team.<ref name="db-ol>[http://www.databaseolympics.com/players/playerpage.htm?ilkid=URIZARUB01 Profile: "Rub<U+00E9>n Uriza"] ''databaseOlympics.com''<small> (Retrieved on January 19, 2008)</small/></ref> He also received a silver medal in ''Individual Jumping''. 

